 블로그를 만들어 보자  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>나만의 블로그를 만들어 보자 💪🏻</h2>\n<p>벨로그, 티스토리, 미디움 등 좋은 블로그 사이트 들이 많지만 서치를 하다보면 ‘개발자스럽게’ 커스터마이징된 블로그들이 많이 보였다. 그래서 만들어본 <a href=\"https://gparkkii.github.io\"><strong>나만의 블로그</strong></a> 👀</p>\n<p>직접 커스터마이징해서 홈페이지를 만들 수도 있겠지만 시간도 많이 걸리고 좋은 템플릿들도 많기 때문에 눈여겨봤던 <a href=\"https://github.com/JaeYeopHan/gatsby-starter-bee\"><strong>gatsby-starter-bee</strong></a> 로 블로그를 만들기로 결정했다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"-todo-list\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-todo-list\" aria-label=\" todo list permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📍 Todo List</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>정적 사이트 생성기인 <code class=\"language-text\">Jekyll</code> 또는 <code class=\"language-text\">Gatsby</code>를 이용해서 블로그를 만든다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">github pages</code> 또는 <code class=\"language-text\">netlify</code>로 호스팅을 한다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">google search console</code>을 이용해서 검색엔진에 등록하기</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"1-gatsby-및-템플릿-설치하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-gatsby-%EB%B0%8F-%ED%85%9C%ED%94%8C%EB%A6%BF-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"1 gatsby 및 템플릿 설치하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. Gatsby 및 템플릿 설치하기</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"-정적-사이트란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EC%A0%95%EC%A0%81-%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\" 정적 사이트란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>💡 정적 사이트란?</h3>\n<p>정적 사이트 (Static Site)는 HTML, CSS, JavaScript로만 이뤄진 사이트다.\n보통 동적인 사이트들은 사용자의 인터랙션에 따라 웹 페이지가 바뀌어가지만 <strong>정적인 웹 페이지는 항상 같은 내용을 보여주기 때문에 구축이 쉽고 속도가 빠르다는 장점이 있다.</strong>\n—> 기업 사이트 또는 개인 포폴 사이트에 많이 쓰인다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"why-gatsby\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#why-gatsby\" aria-label=\"why gatsby permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>why Gatsby?</h3>\n<p>보통 정적사이트 생성기는 <code class=\"language-text\">Jekyll</code> 또는 <code class=\"language-text\">Gatsby</code>가 많이 쓰인다.</p>\n<p>Jekyll은 <code class=\"language-text\">Ruby</code> 기반으로 만들어져 있고\nGatsby는 <code class=\"language-text\">React</code> 기반으로 만들어져 있다.</p>\n<p>Ruby는 한번도 사용해본적이 없기에 익숙한 React 기반의 Gatsby를 선택했다.\n—> Gatsby가 속도도 빠르고 React, GraphQL 기반으로 많은 사람들의 관심과 사랑을 받고 있다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"clone-gatsby-starter-bee\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#clone-gatsby-starter-bee\" aria-label=\"clone gatsby starter bee permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>clone gatsby-starter-bee</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-starter-bee</code>말고 다른 스타일의 템플릿을 원한다면 <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/starters?\"><strong>Gatsby Starters</strong></a> 페이지에서 서치하면 된다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"gatsby-starter-bee-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gatsby-starter-bee-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"gatsby starter bee 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-starter-bee 설치</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">npm install gatsby<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>cli\ngatsby <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">my</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span>blog<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>starter https<span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>github<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>com<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>JaeYeopHan<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>gatsby<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>starter<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>bee</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"develop-files\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#develop-files\" aria-label=\"develop files permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>develop files</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">cd my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>blog<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>starter<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>\nnpm start\n# open localhost<span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">8000</span></code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"2-gatsby-blog-repository-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-gatsby-blog-repository-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"2 gatsby blog repository 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Gatsby Blog Repository 생성</h2>\n<p>Github Pages로 배포하기 위해서는 <code class=\"language-text\">${my github id}.github.io</code> 라는 레포지토리를 생성한다.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.velog.io/images/gparkkii/post/8693822f-8aa4-4af9-b965-dfd76addcdc4/%E1%84%89%E1%85%B3%E1%84%8F%E1%85%B3%E1%84%85%E1%85%B5%E1%86%AB%E1%84%89%E1%85%A3%E1%86%BA%202021-05-20%20%E1%84%8B%E1%85%A9%E1%84%92%E1%85%AE%205.48.22.png\">\n레포지토리를 만들고 난 후 설치한 <code class=\"language-text\">my-blog-starter</code>에서 <code class=\"language-text\">git bash</code>를 실행시켜 해당 폴더의 git 정보를 초기화 해준다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">rm <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>rf <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>git\ngit init</code></pre></div>\n<p>이후 아래 명령어로 내 <code class=\"language-text\">repository</code>에 <code class=\"language-text\">push</code>를 해준다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">git add <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\ngit commit <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>m <span class=\"token string\">\"Init blog project\"</span>\ngit remote add origin https<span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>github<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>com<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>$<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>Github_ID<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>$<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>Git_Repository_Name<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>git\ngit push <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>u origin master</code></pre></div>\n<p>여기까지 진행했다면 <code class=\"language-text\">${Github_ID}.github.io</code>로 접속했을 시 해당 레포지토리의 Readme.md 파일이 뜬다.</p>\n<p>🚀 배포 성공!!</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"3-gatsby-blog-커스텀하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-gatsby-blog-%EC%BB%A4%EC%8A%A4%ED%85%80%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"3 gatsby blog 커스텀하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. Gatsby Blog 커스텀하기</h2>\n<h3 id=\"packagejson-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#packagejson-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"packagejson 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>package.json 설정</h3>\n<p>우선 package.json 파일로 들어가 괄호쳐놓은 name, description, url 등의 부분을 자신의 정보에 맞게 수정한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// package.json</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"gparkkii.io\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"private\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"description\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Gparkkii's Dev Note\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"version\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"0.1.0\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"author\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Gparkkii[JiYeonPark]&lt;jyp933@gmail.com>\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"bugs\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"url\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"https://github.com/gparkkii/gparkkii.github.io/issues\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"homepage\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"https://gparkkii.github.io\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"keywords\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"gatsby\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"license\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"MIT\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"main\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"n/a\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"repository\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"git\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"url\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"git+https://github.com/gparkkii/gparkkii.github.io.git\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"gatsbymetaconfig-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gatsbymetaconfig-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"gatsbymetaconfig 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby.meta.config 설정</h3>\n<p>gatsby.meta.config